{"tid":1578191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全世界嘅關公都唔敢接政府個job，幫政府洗底","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T06:55:23.000Z","uid":50562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b73369cdb5af62ab90a3e5650489f37d8f21ad","tid":1578191,"uid":50562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"全世界嘅關公都唔敢接政府個job，幫政府洗底 sosad<br />\n<br />\nThe Holmes Report has obtained a copy of the brief (excerpted below), which calls for strategic communication advice to &quot;address negative perceptions in key markets overseas to maintain confidence in Hong Kong&quot; and to &quot;underscore the strengths and attributes that differentiate Hong Kong from other cities in the region and bring out the success of 'one country, two systems'.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nAccording to a spokesperson for the Hong Kong government, &quot;The Information Services Department (ISD) carried out a quotation exercise to procure services for external promotion. The quotation exercise lapsed as no bid was received by the close of the quotation period.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nCarrie Lam's government has come in for sustained criticism over its response to the protestors, highlighted by such media gaffes as visiting broken MTR turnstiles while refusing to acknowledge the injuries suffered by protestors.<br />\n<br />\n...the protestors have utilised technology and visual content to build a vibrant, grassroots movement. &quot;Basically this is a political problem not a PR problem,&quot; said another agency source. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.holmesreport.com/latest/article/revealed-failed-hong-kong-govt-pr-plan-to-salvage-global-reputation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.holmesreport.com%2Flatest%2Farticle%2Frevealed-failed-hong-kong-govt-pr-plan-to-salvage-global-reputation&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=cf7b7dad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.holmesreport.com/latest/article/revealed-failed-hong-kong-govt-pr-plan-to-salvage-global-reputation</a>"},{"pid":"450614bd11fb5b35dd2198514bdd3ad327769b19","tid":1578191,"uid":47905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"人民日報做咪得"},{"pid":"e05fa4d7e833e879adb33c6cae509266e2c31118","tid":1578191,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"7b14a5f0e22732d3c2f485f60320480702a6f49f","tid":1578191,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"行頭最top嗰個都諗唔到計幫你啦"},{"pid":"48a8a1289bea0de3f40e7902555d665f08e600f1","tid":1578191,"uid":323412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"人都殺埋仲想人點幫佢洗？"},{"pid":"6c271de4ca7f90bac1b9088114af5f5ae8c24207","tid":1578191,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"公關"},{"pid":"f9330ee200f720cefdd53ed618c5e9f8eba7d2f2","tid":1578191,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:25:48.000Z","msg":"殺撚左人點公關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f84b94778b2dbd81beca344cf06bde1e9a23eb7","tid":1578191,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:27:24.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過搵民記"},{"pid":"633fb659667acdf2ee06bb4d5213c9ab56748ff3","tid":1578191,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"有公司肯接佢係咪會講哂所有野出黎先..."},{"pid":"3061eb387498c8de46dae206b89ca0d0a6c630c8","tid":1578191,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"我哋接咗佢啦"},{"pid":"5600dd0be450f0f9deafa5812abafbc40d7a4869","tid":1578191,"u